import React from 'react'
import { FeatureBody, FeatureSection } from '../MainSection/FeaturesElements'
import NavigationBar from '../Navigation/NavigationBar'
import BarChart from './BarChart'
import LineChart from './LineChart'

function DashBoard() {
    const dashBoard={
        isDashBoard:true
    }

    return (
        <>
            <NavigationBar {...dashBoard} />
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#f4f4f4'>
            
            <BarChart bgColor='#000'/>
            </FeatureBody>
            <FeatureBody bgColor='#0F293D'>
            <LineChart />
            </FeatureBody>
        </>

    )
}

export default DashBoard
